name: Creative Chaos
description: This freestyle adventure illustration was created with no prior planning, colour scheme or concept other than to let my mind run free. Creative Chaos is the second work in a reflective series focused on the evolution of the characters synonymous with my style. The series is dubbed GHETTO SCANS due to the illustrations being scanned in on a brother printer I found on the side of the road. I think it adds to the rawness and overall flavor.
